title: Migration before Uniswap?
body: Due to the nature of the Token, should the Token be listed on Uniswap or should the Migration occur first? If Uniswap is done first, I am very aware that the token may just get sold straight away and the holders will get REKT.
author: 0xeB422361C73Ef9974A6Dd0b957bcC5b6193B36A1
